#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.rebalance.rebalance:1 of
msgid "Make data more balanced across entire cluster."
msgstr "使数据在整个集群中更加均衡。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.rebalance.rst
msgid "参数"
