" chunks * factor."
msgstr "指定平衡后的块数量为输入块总数乘以该因子。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.rebalance.rebalance:8 of
msgid "Specified so the number of chunks are at most num_partitions."
msgstr "指定块的数量最多为 num_partitions。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.rebalance.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.rebalance.rebalance:12 of
